{"tid":1364310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【災難！】香港6月出口貨值大跌9%　遠遜預期","createTime":"2019-07-25T10:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T11:00:03.000Z","uid":33307,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e432679a126bfaa680f61755087f231402c26df5","tid":1364310,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:30:15.000Z","msg":"政府統計處公布，6月香港整體出口貨值按年大跌9%，遠遜預期跌2.3%，5月則跌2.4%，連跌8個月。與此同時，6月整體進口貨值按年亦大跌7.5%。 <br />\n<br />\n出口地區方面，輸往亞洲的整體出口貨值按年下跌8.4%。跌幅最大依次為泰國(跌13.6%)、中國內地(跌10.6%)、韓國(跌8.4%)、馬來西亞(跌7.8%)和日本(跌6.5%)。另一方面，輸往菲律賓和台灣的整體出口貨值則錄得升幅，分別上升33.2%和13.9%。 <br />\n<br />\n同期，來自大部分主要供應地的進口貨值同均錄得下跌，跌幅依次為韓國(跌25.7%)、印度(跌17.4%)、台灣(跌10.8%)、馬來西亞(跌9.0%)和泰國(跌8.2%)。來自內地的進口貨值亦下跌2.3%。另一方面，來自瑞士的進口貨值則上升2.4%。 <br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，全球經濟環境欠佳及中美貿易摩擦，令亞洲的製造業活動和貿易往來進一步受壓，輸往大部分主要市場的出口均錄得不同程度的跌幅。展望將來，環球經濟偏軟，以及中美貿易摩擦及其他外圍發展帶來的不確定性，將繼續制約香港商品出口的表現。"},{"pid":"37db3fd80553258a3c9aba2ec97d7bf7e34d7525","tid":1364310,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:32:56.000Z","msg":"是咪金融xx"},{"pid":"41cb4a8f279cfc8c601004e5fb0604126cf38c77","tid":1364310,"uid":128522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:34:38.000Z","msg":"主要係全世界聖誕單少左好多<br />\n咁樣經香港入大陸既錢, 然後經香港出口既野都會趺"},{"pid":"f9963a834f03c9aaa943f383a7232279696cce76","tid":1364310,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港爆<br />\n<br />\n請AA9們快趣昆老實人落疊買樓<br />\n<br />\n呃埋你最後一餐狗飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ce2c76ab4af4c3d0d4082c1465e8f36a7a911f","tid":1364310,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdef5755b1ce787aaff8867af40ccaef813ea502","tid":1364310,"uid":25601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"但今個月我見葵涌碼頭d貨櫃多左好多"},{"pid":"55cc7d2449cf0e63ad542e933e0eb46e0cadc863","tid":1364310,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fdef5755b1ce787aaff8867af40ccaef813ea502","tid":1364310,"uid":25601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"但今個月我見葵涌碼頭d貨櫃多左好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:40:32.000Z","msg":"但機場空運少咗貨"},{"pid":"10f3856dd3fa53dcbd6a8a6aa44de400b127f43c","tid":1364310,"uid":171504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:41:54.000Z","msg":"新死線！唔好俾港府回氣<br />\n<br />\n【記住條formula】死線已定，728不排除升級！置頂！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363572</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n726 5點 交代上環元朗 針對黑警<br />\n728 2點 回應五大訴求 針對政權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/70hg0QQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F70hg0QQ.jpg&h=5f3b0a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NEtPBpe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNEtPBpe.jpg&h=d22be929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8vuBph.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8vuBph.jpg&h=f992e9fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d485319dad4fde0fc003fd072a182c5f525c7c98","tid":1364310,"uid":1400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:58:09.000Z","msg":"係咪佔中嘅錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ff0617bd4c5433cceecf594439aad8987eaad4","tid":1364310,"uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:58:39.000Z","msg":"source？"},{"pid":"3b66126c1fb38d39526b00634d778284ea7ef15a","tid":1364310,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" cla